lead_paragraph: PAOK Salonika's Croatian coach Igor Tudor said he would not quit despite a shock 2-1 defeat at relegation-threatened Panthrakikos on Sunday that could damage their hopes of a place in Europe.

headline.print_headline: PAOK Manager Tudor Refuses to Quit After Latest Setback
